title: #6 Vols Sweep Tennessee Tech, Advance to NCAA Second Round - University of Tennessee Athletics
content: #6 Vols Sweep Tennessee Tech, Advance to NCAA Second Round  University of Tennessee Athletics
description: A 4-0 sweep of Tennessee Tech Friday afternoon for the No. 6 Tennessee men's tennis team advances the Vols to the round of 32 in the NCAA Tournament. Tennessee will face 21st-ranked Duke Saturday at 1 p.m. ET.
